description.en: CHEQD NETWORK are building the trusted/authentic data economy. CHEQD NETWORK‘s solution enables new business models, where verifiable credentials are exchanged in a trusted, reusable, safer, and cheaper way. We're making it easier to create authentic data ecosystems through customisable commercial models and governance structures, all built upon a public permissionless network with a dedicated token for payment.
